Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:19.23,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:25.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有星光的迷宫里挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:30.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:35.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受灵魂的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:41.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙正在呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:46.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负伤痕 知晓孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:52.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了羁绊的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:55.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除阴翳眼眸中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:57.69,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安和困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:04.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:08.03,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士们 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:10.70,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:14.12,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果背负的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:16.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够称为爱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:18.75,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士们相互支持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:21.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为风的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:25.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的Ω神话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.97,0:01:31.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:20.70,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 没事吗 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小马座藏匿的那群人之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 终于找到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告诉我们 你们藏在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马座？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在看哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你们背后可是门户大开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么天马座他们会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那个叫什么米拉的 害我根本不在状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止克勒利斯一派 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要同时应付天马座他们 太棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.25,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞勒涅（Selene），名字来源于希腊神话月亮女神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞勒涅 没受伤吧   
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圣斗士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诅咒的圣衣！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小马座的圣斗士！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找未失去时间的人类的士兵传来的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们凑巧发现了天马座等人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说正在逼近这座城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马座等人会由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忒拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这任务 请务必交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 我一定会击败那群软弱的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙是我的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忒拜 不许你横插一枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是我的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 不准他们再向前一步 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你二人给我好好迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我是想帮克勒利斯包扎一下伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你这份温柔的心意已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:06:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这份心意足以治愈我的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以塞勒涅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做危险的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 竟能见到天马座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 请问您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是克勒利斯 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.50,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯（Celeris），希腊神话中的名马，小马座出典的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Equuleus小马座的克勒利斯    
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Equuleus小马座…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小马座是闪耀在天马座旁边 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被称作是天马座的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教啊 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是兄弟不如说是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯 快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 有话一会儿再说 上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 抱歉我们在赶路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去帕拉斯的城堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更该上车了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塞勒涅 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是昴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的名字都好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在童话里听过这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一个人孤军奋战…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在前面的隧道下车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 那些人不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 为了保证安全 他们会走其他的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是有滑轮车的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以走其他的楼梯 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这边比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 你抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 免了吧 我一个人也能下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞勒涅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些拥有强大小宇宙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间没有被停止 逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到距离城堡如此之近的地下 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这么多幸存者…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到刻斗士的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:09:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城里的绝大多数人的时间都被夺去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些死里逃生的人们 便藏身此处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艰难维生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你并非为了雅典娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了这些人而战…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我很清楚雅典娜的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来 距离帕拉斯的城堡最近的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理应去冲锋陷阵的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小马座的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您身上圣衣的宿命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些破事都是迷信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 塞勒涅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给天马座他们沏点茶 好好招待着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓库 我去把上面的门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你刚才说的小马座的宿命是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前略有耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小马座是被诅咒的圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身披小马座圣衣者将被引向死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上那圣衣 就会死的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说 小马座圣斗士以获得强大的力量为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定将在战斗中失去生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何还要穿上那圣衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为即使以命相赌 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想得到力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你大概是不会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身上流淌着神之血 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还叫嚷着“不需要神之血”的你 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯真正的目的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不分对象地见人就咬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这话是什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 只需要说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接过来就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞勒涅 也给我来一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯 你也该解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们带到这里来的理由了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座地下城与帕拉斯城是相通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与帕拉斯城相通…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生成长在这座城市 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座不知建成于何时的地下城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像迷宫一般迂回深入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直延伸到帕拉斯所在的城堡附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了 一口气直捣帕拉斯的城堡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能阻止刻斗士的进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能保护许多生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我已经下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会让这里的任何人受到一丝一毫的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 搞什么啊 真让我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为你是为了追求强大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才穿上那身圣衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来只是个没种的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为了保护大家 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得这样 遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为了我们拼命战斗 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个勇敢的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去把帕拉斯打得找不着北
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像被那些刻斗士跟踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石召唤 恶魔之锤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士和苟延残喘的人类们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们藏在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给老子滚出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我跑了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会立刻把他们赶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在这里保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 你也留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你的钢铁圣衣损伤太严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟过来也是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是累赘？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边就交给他们吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好珍惜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从地下来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 又是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原话奉还 你这软骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我打！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到人类竟潜伏到了通往城堡的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能从这里入侵城堡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 当然也能从城堡来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭我的耳朵 轻易就可探出正确的路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也不知道就跟了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈提从地下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷从地上 一同夹击 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美的作战策略
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈提
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会让你胡作非为的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那破烂圣衣还能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然以小宇宙为盾牌弹开了短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的短剑可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱来的是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着破损的圣衣还想正面迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对圣衣的那份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经传递给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被穿着受诅咒的圣衣的家伙说教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没有说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它没有被诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这圣衣想要保护生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小马座圣衣当人陷入绝境 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千钧一发时就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是向弱者伸出援助之手的 十分体贴的圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群星在失去生命之前 会绽放更强烈的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小马座圣斗士也是同样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就在发光后 徒然死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔之锤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电·赫拉克勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈提那小子 到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮炽焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣龙卷风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子可不管哈提那小子的死活了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你们全部轰飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忒拜那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把我们都轰飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体给我撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被卷进去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勒利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看未必
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本不想用这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这招实在太大又难控制 是禁断的奥义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你所说的强大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前问过我 为什么会变强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有了应守护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去需要保护的人时 确实可能强大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有应守护之人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份强大无法估量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱糟糟一堆废话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大小行星（Gigantic Asteroid）！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰鸣吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户绝灭！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我软弱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷我软弱吗！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应守护的人 是你让我察觉到了那份强大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小马座的光辉引导的 是死亡的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互交织的纽带不再迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在克勒利斯炽热的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震动着昴的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 穿上青铜圣衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣衣、传承！小马座的昴、诞生！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
